                    <paragraph id="3.260">
                        <content>
                            <p>
                                <t>In our delegation's view, the moratorium plays a significant role in the increasing digitalization of cross-border trade. Based on our discussions, Chile has reached the conclusion that there is ample evidence confirming the importance of not imposing customs duties on electronic transmissions, as the moratorium benefits businesses, especially micro, small and medium-sized enterprises, which drive the global economy and require greater certainty for their business plans. Therefore, we hope, as others have said before us, that we can have a decision on the moratorium as soon as possible.</t>
