                        <content>
                            <p>
                                <t>We thank the Chair for his report and align with the statement from the SVEs. We thank all Members for their constructive engagement around landing a Ministerial decision on small economies that recognizes work undertaken and lays the groundwork for some concrete areas for discussion between MC13 and MC14.</t>
                            </p>
                        </content>
                    </paragraph>
                    <!--STATEMENT PARAGRAPH 4.20-->
                    <paragraph id="4.20">
                        <content>
                            <p>
                                <t>There are three key elements in the Ministerial decision that reflects the priorities of SVEs. These are areas that are key to helping us to grow through trade and better use trade rules and trade policies to address the impacts of the polycrises which affect the most vulnerable the hardest.</t>
                            </p>
                        </content>
                    </paragraph>
                    <!--STATEMENT PARAGRAPH 4.21-->
                    <paragraph id="4.21">
                        <content>
                            <p>
                                <t>A key part of delivering on our mandate is to work with other relevant international organizations and actors, including the private sector, to help us better address our trade related constraints. Going forward we also want to better use the platform of the CTD to ignite and engender concrete proposals and interactions in other parts of the house. We are keen to work with our partners in WTO to continue to add value to the discussions in the dedicated session in a tangible way. Again, we thank all Members for continuing to support the priorities of SVEs.</t>
                            </p>
                        </content>
                    </paragraph>
                </statement_content>
                <!--STATEMENT INFO-->
                <statement_info>
