                            <p>
                                <t>The draft Ministerial Decision adopted at the 1 December CTD Session for Small Economies, would not have been possible without the support of all Members. It is equally encouraging to hear Ministers in the Mini-Ministerial this week making reference to the outcome. We look forward to the adoption of this draft Ministerial Decision for Small Economies in this General Council to be presented for the consideration of our Ministers in Abu Dhabi.</t>
                            </p>
                        </content>
                    </paragraph>
                </statement_content>
