                            <p>
                                <t>We thank the African Group for presenting this topic of utmost importance. We would like to highlight that some international commitments made by developing countries in different agreements and organizations may not by fulfilled without the help of specific technologies. It is also important to bear in mind that without transfer of technology certain developing countries may remain at the margin of the international trade system for longer than necessary.</t>
                            </p>
