                            <p>
                                <t>Brazil is a supporter of the discussions of trade and transfer of technology in the Working Group. We also welcome Chile's interest as Chair of the Working Group to see it strengthened, including by encouraging Members to submit more proposals – to have more in-depth discussions on this relevant issue. We welcome proposals that will strengthen the Working Group and will make it more relevant within the WTO structure. The idea of perhaps having a discussion that is horizontal and that addresses the different aspects of the bodies makes sense. We have not seen the draft decision yet, so we will wait for a document, so we can express positions that are more in detail. The overall trust of this initiative seems to go in a positive direction.</t>
                            </p>
                        </content>
                    </paragraph>
