                        <content>
                            <p>
                                <t>The United States requests that the European Union suspend implementation of this regulation until it has been notified to the WTO TBT Committee and to provide adequate time for stakeholder comment and take those comments into account before implementing the final regulation.</t>
                            </p>
                        </content>
                    </paragraph>
                </statement_content>
