                            </p>
                        </content>
                    </paragraph>
                    <!--STATEMENT PARAGRAPH 19.21-->
                    <paragraph id="19.21">
                        <content>
                            <p>
                                <t>Increasing recourse to trade related climate and environment measures also made in depth multilateral discussions on these matters urgent, in order to limit their negative trade effects, to ensure that they do not constitute arbitrary or disguised restrictions or unjustifiable discrimination in international trade, while ensuring their compliance with both international trade and environment law. Considering that countries carry out different climate policies within the context of their own national conditions and development levels, we believe that a holistic perspective and a transparent basis should be created in which heterogeneous climate policies can be compared and eventually aligned, also taking into account needs of sustainable development.</t>
                            </p>
                        </content>
                    </paragraph>
                    <!--STATEMENT PARAGRAPH 19.22-->
                    <paragraph id="19.22">
                        <content>
                            <p>
