                            </p>
                        </content>
                    </paragraph>
                    <!--STATEMENT PARAGRAPH 19.23-->
                    <paragraph id="19.23">
                        <content>
                            <p>
                                <t>We would like to indicate that we support deeper discussions on the nexus of trade and environment at the WTO, be it through informal sessions or dedicated discussions, and we are ready to constructively engage with other members.</t>
