                    <!--STATEMENT PARAGRAPH 19.62-->
                    <paragraph id="19.62">
                        <content>
                            <p>
                                <t>Norway would like to thank China and Colombia for their engagement on enhancing the multilateral deliberative function on environment-related trade measures and fostering sustainable development. Two comments: We support a strong political commitment to multilateral cooperative approaches coming out of MC13 and strengthening further the role of the CTE in this regard. A deliberative discussion in the CTE must take into regard also the need for environmental measures and the right to regulate. Ambitious multilateral action would reduce the need for unilateral measures.</t>
